<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xml:lang="en"
      xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
      xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
      xmlns:i18n="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/i18n"
      lang="en"
         metal:use-macro="context/prefs_main_template/macros/master"
         i18n:domain="ade25.widgets">

<body>

<div metal:fill-slot="prefs_configlet_main">

    <div metal:use-macro="context/global_statusmessage/macros/portal_message">
        Portal status message
    </div>

    <div class="o-page--control-panel configlet">
        <div class="o-page__header">
            <h1 class="o-page__title o-page__title--primary" i18n:translate="">
                Ade25 Widgets Settings
            </h1>
            <p class="o-page__abstract">
                Configure and setup content widgets
            </p>
            <a id="setup-link" class="c-button c-button--default link-parent"
                     tal:attributes="href string:${portal_url}/@@overview-controlpanel"
                     i18n:translate="label_up_to_plone_setup">
                Up to Site Setup
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="o-page__main">
            <div class="c-page__header">
                <div class="c-page-header__title">
                    <h2 class="c-page-header__headline" i18n:translate="">
                        Control panels
                    </h2>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="o-page__section o-page__section--spacer">
                <div class="app-control-panels">
                <div class="o-page__section app-control-panel">
                    <h3 class="app-control-panel__title" i18n:translate="">
                        Widget Setup
                    </h3>
                    <p>Configure available content widgets and setup panel page slots.</p>
                    <div class="app-control-panel__action">
                        <a class="app-button app-button--default link-parent"
                                 tal:attributes="href string:${portal_url}/@@ade25-widgets-settings-base"
                                 i18n:translate="">
                            Configure
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="o-page__section app-control-panel">
                    <h3 class="app-control-panel__title" i18n:translate="">
                        Content Widgets
                    </h3>
                    <p>Configure individual content widgets</p>
                    <div class="app-control-panel__action">
                        <a class="app-button app-button--default link-parent"
                                 tal:attributes="href string:${portal_url}/@@ade25-widgets-settings-widgets"
                                 i18n:translate="">
                            Configure
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="o-page__footer">
            <div class="o-page__section o-page__section--spacer">
                <div class="c-alert c-alert--danger">
                    <h4 class="c-alert__title">Danger Zone</h4>
                    <p>In order to update the available widgets and their corrsponding settings, it is possible to export the configuration as a plain JSON file and update the contents accordingly. Please be aware that a badly formatted file or errors in the required settings could damage the site beyond recovery. You have been warned.</p>
                    <p><a class="c-button c-button--primary" tal:attributes="href python:context.absolute_url() + '/@@ade25-widgets-export-settings'">Export JSON</a></p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
